OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) is to probe into
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police's investigation
OL,9,Fto find a vulnerable missing person,
OL,10,Fwho was later found dead.
OL,12,FShahab Uddin who was 40, was found
OL,13,Fnear the village of Quorn in
OL,14,FLeicestershire on 21st August 2025,
OL,15,Feight days after he was first reported
OL,16,Fmissing by family members who had
OL,17,Fbecome concerned about him.
