OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,FHundreds of volunteers helped search
OL,7,Ffor him alongside police specialist
OL,8,Fsearch teams, drone searches and a
OL,9,Fpolice helicopter.
OL,11,FMr Uddin was described as "very
OL,12,Fvulnerable because he has learning
OL,13,Fdifficulties" and in need of his
OL,14,Fmedication, as during the initial
OL,15,Fsearches, it was feared he might not
OL,16,Fhave taken it for more than 24 hours.
OL,18,FLeicestershire Police received a
OL,19,Fpublic complaint in relation to their
OL,20,Finitial response.
