OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,FAfter Mr Uddin's death, the force made
OL,7,Fa mandatory referral to the police
OL,8,Fwatchdog the IOPC - the standard
OL,9,Fpractice in such circumstances - and
OL,10,Ffor the Professional Standards
OL,11,FDepartment to investigate.
OL,13,FDuring the force's investigation, the
OL,14,Fenquiries led to a further referral
OL,15,Fbeing made by the force to the IOPC.
OL,17,FAn independent investigation
OL,19,FFollowing this second referral, the
OL,20,FIPOC has now confirmed it will carry
OL,21,Fout an independent investigation.
