OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,FThe complaint relates to the
OL,7,Fcommunication by police with Mr
OL,8,FUddin's family members, and to the
OL,9,Fforce's actions and enquiries made
OL,10,Fduring the time he was missing.
OL,12,FThe IOPC says Mr Uddin's family have
OL,13,Fraised concerns around whether Mr
OL,14,FUddin's race, religion and disability
OL,15,Fwas any kind of factor in the way
OL,16,Fofficers treated the search.
OL,18,FIOPC Director Emily Barry said: "Our
OL,19,Fthoughts and sympathies go to the
OL,20,Ffamily and friends of Mr Uddin and
OL,21,Feveryone affected by his tragic death.
