OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,F"Our investigation is examining the
OL,7,Fcomplaint made by Mr Uddin's family in
OL,8,Frelation to the police response to the
OL,9,Fmissing person report.
OL,11,F"This involves looking at the actions
OL,12,Fand decisions of Leicestershire Police
OL,13,Ffollowing the calls made to the force
OL,14,Fabout the concerns for Mr Uddin's
OL,15,Fwelfare and subsequent missing
OL,16,Fperson's report.
