OL,3,CPolice watchdog to examine force's
OL,4,Cresponse to report of missing man
OL,6,F"We are also considering if risk
OL,7,Fassessments were assessed, graded and
OL,8,Fmanaged appropriately and concerns
OL,9,Ffrom Mr Uddin's family about whether
OL,10,Fthe officers treated the search for Mr
OL,11,FUddin differently because of his race,
OL,12,Freligion and disability."
OL,14,FIOPC investigators have been in
OL,15,Fcontact with Mr Uddin's family to
OL,16,Fexplain the role and to advise them of
OL,17,Fthe next steps.
